Impala Platinum Plans to Cut Jobs at Marula as Mine Fails to Meet Targets

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-05-27T08:03:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-27/impala-platinum-plans-to-cut-jobs-at-marula-as-mine-fails-to-meet-targets.html
Impala Platinum Holdings Ltd. (IMP)  said it
will cut jobs at its Marula Platinum Ltd. unit because the
operation continues to underperform against its targets.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
